        "Description": "Hello, 47\r\rYour target today is Torres Poimbo he was a local cannabis dealer in Sapienza, but he  has been climbing the ranks of the Albanian Mafia on the Amalfi Coast since you were last there, he has plans to take revenge on the our client who has ordered both contracts on the Albanian Mafia.\r\r Our client wants you to poison him, because as he says:\r\r&quot;The Albanians have poisoned Europe for long enough time to see how  it feels to be poisoned!&quot;\r\rGood Luck, 47.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.",
